+<html lang="ta">
+<head>
+<meta charset="utf-8">
+<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1">
+<title>Reading Notes &amp; Section Bookmarks | Om Saravana Bhava</title>
+<meta name="description" content="Manage browser-local personal notes and heading bookmarks for eligible OmSaravanaBhava literature routes without storing selected devotional text.">
+<meta name="robots" content="index,follow">
+<link rel="canonical" href="https://omsaravanabhava.org/reading-notes.html">
+<link rel="stylesheet" href="assets/css/osb44.css">
+<link rel="stylesheet" href="assets/css/reading-notes.css">
+<link rel="icon" href="favicon.svg" type="image/svg+xml">
+<meta name="theme-color" content="#a51d17">
+<link rel="manifest" href="manifest.json">
+<script defer src="assets/js/pwa-register.js"></script>
+</head>
+<body data-release="224">
+<a href="#main-content" class="skip-link">Skip to main content</a>
+<div class="top">🛕 ஓம் சரவணபவ · Browser-local reading notes and section bookmarks</div>
+<nav class="nav" aria-label="Primary navigation"><div class="nav-inner">
+<a class="brand" href="index.html" aria-label="Om Saravana Bhava home">ஓம் சரவணபவ</a>
+<div class="links"><a href="discovery.html">Discover</a><a href="reading-workspace.html">Reading Workspace</a><a href="reading-notes.html" aria-current="page">Notes</a><a href="reading-list.html">Reading List</a><a href="print-pdf.html">Print &amp; PDF</a></div>
+</div></nav>
+<main id="main-content" class="wrap">
+<nav aria-label="Breadcrumb"><p><a href="index.html">Home</a> › <a href="reading-workspace.html">Reading Workspace</a> › <span aria-current="page">Reading Notes</span></p></nav>
+
+<section class="card reading-notes-hero">
+<div>
+<span class="pill">Release 224 · Local notes and bookmarks</span>
+<h1 class="section-title" lang="ta">வாசிப்பு குறிப்புகள்</h1>
+<h2>Reading Notes &amp; Section Bookmarks</h2>
+<p>Review your own reflections, questions, practice notes and section bookmarks. Records remain in this browser and do not copy selected devotional text.</p>
+</div>
+<div class="reading-notes-metric"><strong id="readingNotesTotal">0</strong><span>local records</span></div>
+<div class="reading-notes-metric"><strong id="readingNotesRoutes">0</strong><span>reading routes</span></div>
+<div class="reading-notes-metric"><strong id="readingNotesBookmarks">0</strong><span>section bookmarks</span></div>
+<div class="reading-notes-metric"><strong id="readingNotesWritten">0</strong><span>written notes</span></div>
+</section>
+
+<section class="card reading-notes-controls" aria-label="Reading-note filters">
+<label for="readingNotesSearch">Search your notes
+<input id="readingNotesSearch" type="search" placeholder="Tamil or English note text…" autocomplete="off">
+</label>
+<label for="readingNotesKindFilter">Note kind
+<select id="readingNotesKindFilter">
+<option value="all">All note kinds</option>
+</select>
+</label>
+<label for="readingNotesRouteFilter">Reading route
+<select id="readingNotesRouteFilter">
+<option value="all">All reading routes</option>
+</select>
+</label>
+<button class="btn secondary" id="readingNotesReset" type="button">Reset filters</button>
+<button class="btn secondary" id="readingNotesExport" type="button" disabled>Export JSON</button>
+<button class="btn secondary" id="readingNotesClear" type="button" disabled>Clear notes</button>
+</section>
+
+<p id="readingNotesStatus" role="status" aria-live="polite">Loading browser-local notes…</p>
+<section id="readingNotesItems" class="grid reading-notes-grid" aria-label="Reading notes and bookmarks">
+<article class="card">Loading notes…</article>
+</section>
+
+<section class="card reading-notes-boundary-card">
+<h2>Privacy and publication boundary</h2>
+<ul>
+<li>Only your note, route metadata and optional heading label are stored.</li>
+<li>Selected devotional text and page body content are not stored.</li>
+<li>Notes do not modify the published page, source evidence, copyright status or completeness statement.</li>
+<li>Clearing notes preserves reading progress, the reading list, accessibility preferences and audio history.</li>
+<li>No account, analytics, cloud synchronization or collaborative editing is used.</li>
+</ul>
+<p><a class="btn" href="reading-workspace.html">Open Reading Workspace</a></p>
+</section>
+
+<noscript><section class="card" role="status"><h2>JavaScript is disabled</h2><p>Browser-local notes require JavaScript. Existing literature remains available through the <a href="reading-workspace.html">Reading Workspace</a>.</p></section></noscript>
+</main>
+<footer>© Om Saravana Bhava · <a href="reading-notes.html">Reading Notes</a> · <a href="reading-workspace.html">Reading Workspace</a> · <a href="sources.html">Sources &amp; publication policy</a></footer>
+</body>
+</html>
